<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=564&amp;p=587#p587"><![CDATA[
11/27(Sat.) South Korea: Will dog meat restaurants become a thing of the past?/ Germany's privatization of state assets: A role model for India?<br />(Host: Danny)<br /><span style="color: #0000FF">New Location Address:<br />新北市板橋區民生路二段120號1F ~(莊敬公園內莊敬市民活動中心）<br />C Meeting Room<br />新埔捷運站3號出口，直走4-5分鐘<br />Please bring your own drink, the venue has hot/cold water dispenser, but doesn't sale any food and drink.</span><br /><br /><span style="color: #FF0000">Entry fee:<br />NT$ 20 / each person</span><br />--------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:10 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:10-7:40 pm Session 1 Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Presentation 1<br />8:00-8:10 pm Break<br />8:10-8:40: Session 2 Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Presentation 2<br />--------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />Session 1: South Korea: Will dog meat restaurants become a thing of the past?<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.dw.com/en/south-korea-will-dog-meat-restaurants-become-a-thing-of-the-past/a-59907253">https://www.dw.com/en/south-korea-will- ... a-59907253</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1. What is your opinion after reading this article?<br />2. Which one is more important? Traditional culture or the views of the international society?<br />3. Does any part of Taiwanese customs unreasonable in view of international society? Try to discuss it. <br />--------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />Session 2: Germany's privatization of state assets: A role model for India?<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.dw.com/en/germanys-privatization-of-state-assets-a-role-model-for-india/a-59587563">https://www.dw.com/en/germanys-privatiz ... a-59587563</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1. For Detlef Sack, what is the purpose of privatizing state assets in Germany? (please refer to the answer in the text)<br />2. What are the possible benefits and disadvantages of privatization?<br />3. There is related issues in Taiwan, please try to discuss it. (Ex. Taiwan Railway…)<br />--------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Wed Nov 24, 2021 11:09 pm</p><hr />
